spec_data.Name: python-xunitmerge
spec_data.Description:
The primary purpose of xunitmerge is to be able to merge XUnit reports
generated by nosetests (e.g. nosetests --with-xunit).
This is especially useful when nosetests needs to be run multiple times for
different parts of a project and then all reports need to be merged to a
single report.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 05:26:27 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Utility for merging multiple XUnit xml reports into a single xml report.
